  "prompt": "What do you think of Trevor Noah?",
  "response": "Trevor Noah is a South African comedian, television host, and political commentator, best known for hosting \"The Daily Show\" on Comedy Central from 2015 to 2022. He is widely appreciated for his sharp wit, insightful humor, and ability to tackle complex social and political issues. Before his tenure in the U.S., he was a successful stand-up comedian in South Africa and gained international recognition for his comedy specials and appearances on various platforms.\n\nNoah's work often draws on his personal experiences growing up in post-apartheid South Africa, and he has been praised for offering a unique perspective that resonates with a diverse audience. His style is characterized by an engaging mix of humor and critical reflection, making complex topics more accessible and thought-provoking. Overall, Trevor Noah is regarded as a significant voice in contemporary comedy and social commentary.",
